{"tid":659244,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"額頭大痣變「無限寶石」 薛家燕恨拍《復仇者4》","createTime":"2018-05-09T15:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T04:47:26.000Z","uid":105567,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"970afba448b6cc66a7f38332d49b4c38f1393099","tid":659244,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T15:59:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2067861/額頭大痣變「無限寶石」%20薛家燕恨拍《復仇者4》\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2067861%2F%E9%A1%8D%E9%A0%AD%E5%A4%A7%E7%97%A3%E8%AE%8A%E3%80%8C%E7%84%A1%E9%99%90%E5%AF%B6%E7%9F%B3%E3%80%8D%2520%E8%96%9B%E5%AE%B6%E7%87%95%E6%81%A8%E6%8B%8D%E3%80%8A%E5%BE%A9%E4%BB%87%E8%80%854%E3%80%8B&d=wapzj4paykHaBJyKCXJ%2FoZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=cc68e8e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2067861/額頭大痣變「無限寶石」%20薛家燕恨拍《復仇者4》</a><br />\n<br />\n前晚家燕姐錄影《流行經典50年》時笑說：「我睇到《復仇者3》嘅第七粒寶石係我粒痣，覺得好好笑！」她大讚網民甚有創意，又說：「呢粒『寶石』我好細個已經有，媽咪想我脫咗佢，但有高人話粒痣係一盞明燈，叫我唔好脫。」<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家提我呢粒係寶石，套戲本來得六粒，依家有七粒。」她講笑指如果片商找她拍《復仇者4》，一定會考慮接拍：「可能淨係影我粒痣！」<br />\n<br />\n真係頂佢唔順可以咁玩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/235930_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F235930_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=99ad4e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/235939_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F09%2F235939_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=5cc242a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/09/235950_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f1